ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n龍崎知道左邊個係新奇拿 唔即刻制服佢邀功 反而同佢一齊走佬 真係對個新奇拿產生左感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nArma又係唔知點解想幫龍崎 只可以勉強解做日久生情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n須賀原作為特警呀頭 智力級數竟然同松田同級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n龍崎有咩比人睇得出繼承左L又完全表現唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有個超明顯既bug<br />\n筆記持有者應該係接觸到另一本筆記都可以恢復記憶<br />\n<br />\n電影版第二集藤原都只係掂左女主播本筆記就返返黎<br />\n<br />\n但係依集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30b89555526a062def54a89ecfb26db69b4b6c2","tid":40603,"uid":842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"邊到有得睇返舊嗰兩集<br />\niTunes Store都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1040392654cd44cc84bf169a271feecd72d8006","tid":40603,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"靜係想知今集係咪真係有松山研一同藤原龍也份？"},{"pid":"eb7fb9f8e099aeaeda5848563f9057577c80be08","tid":40603,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"最大問題係感覺全部人都蠢過以前d人幾十倍<br />\n好多野又無交代<br />\n而且有一點真係接受唔到<br />\n(劇透黑字左，quote睇）<br />\n[bl